  "title": "Infant Educator | Up to $5K | 5 Days Rotate Shift - 0310",
  "description": "<p>Infant Educator</p><ul><li><p>5 day | 7am - 7pm Rotate shift (44 hour)</p></li><li><p>Salary: $3500 - $5000 + AWS + Performance Bonus + Sign on Bonus $10000 </p></li><li><p>Work location: Islandwide Singapore (Urgent Punggol / Bartley / Tampines) </p></li><li><p>Obtained at least a Certificate in Infant Care (CIT), Advanced Certificate in Early Years (ACEY), Higher Certificate in Infant Care (HCIC), or its equivalent</p></li></ul><p>Interested applicants can also send your resume to (Liwenpoh741#<a href=\"http://gmail.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">gmail.com</a>) and allow our consultant to match you with our clients. No Charges will be incurred by Candidates for any service rendered.</p><p>WA ME <a href=\"tel:9735 4019\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><u><strong>9735 4019</strong></u></a> for more Infant Educator role</p><p><strong>Job Role & Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Plan and carry out the daily programme, developmental and care-giving tasks as assigned</p></li><li><p>Attend to the health, hygiene and safety needs of the infants</p></li><li><p>Create a safe environment and provide the best possible care to infants under their care</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain good rapport with parents</p></li></ul><p>POH LI WEN REG NO: R25136683</p><p>THE SUPREMEHR ADVISORY PTE LTD EA NO: 14C7279</p>",
